### Read trip by id 1 | TripDAO
GET {{url}}/trips/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### ReadAll trips | TripDAO
GET {{url}}/trips
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### create a new trip | TripDAO
POST {{url}}/trips
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "country": "Greece",
  "name": "Island Hopping Adventure",
  "category": "sea",
  "price": 2800.0,
  "start": "2025-12-20T09:00:00",
  "end": "2025-12-25T18:00:00",
  "guideId": 1
}
### Update trip | TripDAO
PUT {{url}}/trips/1
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Island Hopping Adventure (updated)",
  "price": 2950.0
}

### Delete trip | TripDAO
DELETE {{url}}/trips/2
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Accept: application/json

### Link existing guide to trip | TripDAO
PUT {{url}}/trips/3/guides/3
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Accept: application/json

### Filter: only one category
GET {{url}}/trips/category/forest
Accept: application/json

### Get total trip price per guide (US-5)
GET {{url}}/trips/guides/totalprice
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### Packing items for a trip
GET {{url}}/trips/1/packing
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### Total packing weight for a trip
GET {{url}}/trips/1/packing/weight
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

